{"tid":1559422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[911] 2019年, 有幾多人仲相信飛機可以撞穿鋼筋水泥?","createTime":"2019-09-10T20:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T21:57:40.000Z","uid":300741,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"238baf8e3f6f08b3b13e5a9d2fc33bf6e44260e0","tid":1559422,"uid":300741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T20:57:46.000Z","msg":"簡單一句: 飛機所用嘅合金材料都唔係特別硬, 以及為昇空減重金屬質量都唔會高, 尤其係機翼部分, 保證一撞就同機身分離以及粉碎。另一方面因為飛機外殼好薄, 所以飛機撞毀果時基本上會全身粉碎, 物理演算唔可能用飛機撞穿/用機翼切割鋼筋水泥。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物理演算:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjq-yK2ak_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcjq-yK2ak_U&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=d54ebbb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjq-yK2ak_U</a><br />\n<br />\n911事件中沒有飛機被騎劫(粵語)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lmcAAd_mz-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlmcAAd_mz-E&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=66763022\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lmcAAd_mz-E</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科-九一一事件陰謀論<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80%E8%AB%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2599%25B0%25E8%25AC%2580%25E8%25AB%2596&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=f3daf355\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80%E8%AB%96</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論如何, 也許飛機是假的, 但死人是真的。<br />\n<br />\n不求正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;--相信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;--不相信"},{"pid":"d8e11afaa9f79c1be37260eac4be3aac1012ef7b","tid":1559422,"uid":226